  "description": "Marblelous 2 is an action puzzler where you guide up to three marbles to the exit of a level while collecting items on the way. You don't control the marble directly, but through placing arrows on the ground that cause the ball to change direction. You lose a life if the ball collides with a wall or any obstacle. The game offers 100 levels in total and later levels introduce special objects like teleporters, shields or rails. <br><br>The included level editor lets you create your own puzzles. You can also import your own graphics in the game from any paint program.",
